ingham 本書應該唔少人睇過，你簡要咁講咗重點出嚟，<br />\n但最重要係講解咗香港個情況 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無人講出嚟，你睇陳文敏本新書有一篇講法治，講到一舊舊<br />\n<a href=\"https://researchblog.law.hku.hk/2020/03/new-book-by-johannes-chan-righteousness.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresearchblog.law.hku.hk%2F2020%2F03%2Fnew-book-by-johannes-chan-righteousness.html&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNpggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=e22963e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://researchblog.law.hku.hk/2020/03/new-book-by-johannes-chan-righteousness.html</a><br />\n<br />\n早幾年戴妖都出咗本書講，無記錯好似都係無乜料到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b39e5c60205aa07ab6cbfc5598acfee1f6176655","tid":1945273,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T15:12:00.000Z","msg":"【立會要初選 「三不投」聯署】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1945850\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1945850</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F6mpEMQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF6mpEMQ.png&h=b0d9d68a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95c15db00114d3b7017549513cc8e194635b9ce9","tid":1945273,"uid":129990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecaec56904d3475abee1a3d87b22f1012bc620f6","tid":1945273,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90aa0e1af2961706df3c83fb51246056b022d2ca","tid":1945273,"uid":129990,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T02:56:04.000Z","msg":"香港法治冇死，因為從來都冇存在過<br />\n順便幫自己賣下廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小弟個Channel有一條片完整地解釋咗何謂法治，同埋點解香港現行體制之下從來都冇法治。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望幫到唔同人理解啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sQG5WVAp_Tc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsQG5WVAp_Tc&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNpggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=87d60594\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sQG5WVAp_Tc</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T14:32:32.000Z","msg":"我睇咗段片，講得好好喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你整架？<br />\n幫你重開post宣傳吓？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:36:49.000Z","msg":"師兄，條channel係我有份既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先多謝你欣賞我地既努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />台長表示極感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你咁有心幫我地宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當然歡迎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想真知識可以傳開"},{"pid":"b3cae821a1746b143d0f5b90cce6dc275ec7691a","tid":1945273,"uid":311337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:09:24.000Z","msg":"法治已死"},{"pid":"a5f2b23162bba38c2a6dbe5009ab7b44fe135252","tid":1945273,"uid":117332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T13:36:39.000Z","msg":"雖然認同香港唔存在法治，但我認為香港唔民主最多解釋到點解香港無法治。但法治係兼容專制同民主制度。<br />\n法治概念有好大爭議，但幾條比較出名既原則: 1。法律係最高依歸，高於任何權力 2。法律面前人人平等 [3。]保障人權 [4。]彰顯道德(良法先係法律，以前帶耀庭最鍾意講) [5。]三權分立 (我諗出名啲既係孟德斯9)<br />\n<br />\n括號係我唔認同或者唔肯定，我地剩係睇前2樣。香港承襲英治既法律，個啲法律既條文同執行都賦予公權力同政府太大自由裁量權; 而家甚至有法不依<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92552bad13d66e477371dc35548c43167296b099","tid":1945273,"uid":117332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T13:48:23.000Z","msg":"其實法治係乜野，重點又唔係真係法治係乜，因為要介界法治，佢本身唔係一個客觀真理既觀念然後等待被發現。佢只係唔同學派或者政治力量想用佢黎分析國家或者國家既法律，唔同法治既定義係有佢既目的性。<br />\n<br />\n所以中共講佢行緊佢既法治，歐美講自己先係法治，自由派可以講民主係必要於法治，社會主義者可以講三權分立係與不相干。<br />\n<br />\n如果要討論法治咩定義先係合理，咁我諗其中一個係講法矛唔矛盾，或者某啲定義法治係咪仲有效既分析方法(例如良法先係法治就唔係，雖然有人會argue係)<br />\n<br />\n所以，你覺得講法治而死係偽命題，我會覺得。。討論法治本身已經係偽命題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[9up]"},{"pid":"7bc04740c48d67e47b2701865af074c63da0df6b","tid":1945273,"uid":117332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T14:02:27.000Z","msg":"btw, tom bingham既討論方向似係更偏向法治既procedure aspect? 同我既討論方向唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"589b24105724a04feaa9b8f848bc6af0875e6a42","tid":1945273,"uid":30115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T14:14:19.000Z","msg":"仲信香港有法治係咪on 9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}